<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/>
<title>DVR Desktop Review — NOO — {{metadata.orderNumber}}</title>
<style>
  /* ── Design tokens (matched to URAR v2) ───────────────────────────────── */
  :root{
    --navy:#0C2340; --navy-mid:#163D6B; --navy-light:#1F5499;
    --gold:#C49A1A; --gold-bg:#FBF5E0; --gold-light:#F7ECC8;
    --text:#1A1A1A; --muted:#6B7280; --border:#CBD5E1;
    --green:#155F2A; --red:#9B1C1C; --page-w:8.5in;
  }

  /* ── Base ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  body{background:#E5E7EB;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:8pt;color:var(--text);print-color-adjust:exact}

  /* ── Page shell ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────*/
  .page{width:var(--page-w);min-height:11in;background:#fff;margin:0 auto 32px;padding:0.45in 0.5in 0.55in;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.15);page-break-after:always;position:relative}
  .page:last-child{page-break-after:auto}
  @media print{.page{margin:0;box-shadow:none}}

  /* ── Brand header ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .brand-bar{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:8px 14px;margin:0 -0.5in 10px;width:calc(100% + 1in);border-bottom:3px solid var(--gold)}
  .brand-left{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  .brand-name{font-size:15pt;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.08em;color:#fff}
  .brand-name span{color:var(--gold)}
  .brand-sub{font-size:7.5pt;color:#B8C9E0;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:1px}
  .brand-badges{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:3px}
  .brand-badge{font-size:6.5pt;color:var(--gold-light);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,26,.45);padding:1px 6px;border-radius:10px}
  .brand-contact{font-size:6.5pt;color:#B8C9E0;margin-top:2px}

  /* ── Form title bar ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .form-title-bar{background:var(--gold);color:var(--navy);text-align:center;padding:5px 0;margin-bottom:8px;border-radius:2px}
  .form-title-bar h1{font-size:11pt;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase}
  .form-title-bar p{font-size:7.5pt;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy-mid);margin-top:1px}

  /* ── Section headers ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .section-hdr{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;font-size:7.5pt;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;padding:3px 8px;margin:7px 0 3px;border-left:4px solid var(--gold)}
  .section-hdr.gold{background:var(--gold-bg);color:var(--navy);border-left:4px solid var(--gold)}

  /* ── Grid utilities ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .row{display:grid;gap:0;margin-bottom:0}
  .g2{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .g3{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr}
  .g4{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}
  .g5{grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr)}
  .cell{border:1px solid var(--border);padding:3px 6px;line-height:1.4}
  .cell+.cell{border-left:none}
  .lbl{font-size:6.5pt;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;display:block;margin-bottom:1px}
  .val{font-size:8pt;color:var(--text)}

  /* ── Photo box ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .photo-box{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;background:#F1F5F9;min-height:150px;max-height:170px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
  .photo-box img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block}
  .photo-placeholder{font-size:7.5pt;color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding:8px}

  /* ── Values + grade panel ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .top-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:40% 60%;gap:8px;margin-bottom:6px}
  .value-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:6px;padding:3px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
  .value-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .value-lbl{font-size:6.5pt;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0}
  .value-val{font-size:9pt;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);text-align:right}
  .value-sub{font-size:6.5pt;color:var(--muted);text-align:right}
  .value-panel{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;padding:6px 8px;background:#FAFBFC}
  .value-panel-hdr{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;font-size:7pt;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:2px 6px;margin:-6px -8px 5px;border-radius:2px 2px 0 0}

  /* ── Grade badges ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .grade-section{margin-top:5px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden}
  .grade-hdr{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;font-size:7pt;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:2px 6px}
  .grade-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:0}
  .grade-badge{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:4px 2px;border-right:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);cursor:default}
  .grade-badge:last-child{border-right:none}
  .grade-badge{background:#9e9e9e}
  .grade-badge .grade-letter{font-size:14pt;font-weight:900;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);line-height:1}
  .grade-badge .grade-tick{font-size:7pt;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);margin-top:1px}
  .grade-badge.selected.grade-A{background:#1B5E20}
  .grade-badge.selected.grade-B{background:#0D47A1}
  .grade-badge.selected.grade-C{background:#E65100}
  .grade-badge.selected.grade-D{background:#B71C1C}
  .grade-badge.selected .grade-letter{color:#fff;text-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}
  .grade-badge.selected .grade-tick{color:#fff}
  .grade-desc{background:var(--gold-bg);padding:3px 6px;font-size:6pt;color:var(--navy-mid);line-height:1.45}
  .grade-desc span{display:block}

  /* ── Y/N checkboxes ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .yn-box{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:13px;height:13px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);font-size:7.5pt;font-weight:900;color:transparent;border-radius:2px;vertical-align:middle}
  .yn-box.checked{background:var(--navy);border-color:var(--navy);color:#fff}
  .yn-pair{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;font-size:7.5pt;white-space:nowrap}

  /* ── Admin question rows ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .admin-row{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:6px;padding:3px 6px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-top:none;font-size:7.5pt;line-height:1.4}
  .admin-row:first-of-type{border-top:none}
  .admin-row:nth-child(even){background:#F8FAFC}
  .admin-q-num{font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);width:12px;flex-shrink:0;padding-top:1px}
  .admin-q-text{flex:1;color:var(--text)}
  .admin-yn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;flex-shrink:0;padding-top:1px}

  /* ── Comments / text areas ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .comments-box{border:1px solid var(--border);min-height:220px;padding:6px 8px;font-size:7.5pt;color:var(--text);white-space:pre-wrap;background:#FAFBFC;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:8px}

  /* ── Scope paragraphs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .scope-para{font-size:7.5pt;line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:justify;color:var(--text)}
  .scope-para strong{font-weight:700;color:var(--navy)}
  .scope-para em{font-style:italic}
  .scope-para.indent{padding-left:14px}

  /* ── Limiting conditions list ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .condition-list{list-style:none;padding:0;margin-bottom:4px}
  .condition-list li{font-size:7.5pt;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:4px;text-align:justify;padding-left:18px;position:relative}
  .condition-list li::before{content:attr(data-n) ".";position:absolute;left:0;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy)}

  /* ── iAVM disclosure box ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .iavm-box{border:1px solid var(--border);padding:7px 10px;font-size:7.5pt;line-height:1.5;text-align:justify;margin-bottom:8px;background:#FAFBFC;border-radius:2px}

  /* ── Signature block ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .sig-block{border:1px solid var(--border);padding:7px 10px;margin:5px 0;border-radius:3px;background:#FAFBFC}
  .sig-label{font-size:6.5pt;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1px}
  .sig-name{font-size:9pt;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);font-style:italic;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:4px;padding-bottom:4px}
  .sig-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:4px}
  .sig-item{font-size:7pt;color:var(--text)}
  .sig-item b{color:var(--navy)}

  /* ── Continued marker ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .continued{text-align:center;font-size:7.5pt;font-style:italic;color:var(--muted);margin-top:10px}

  /* ── Page footer ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .page-footer{border-top:2px solid var(--navy);margin-top:8px;padding-top:4px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center}
  .page-footer-left{font-size:6.5pt;color:var(--muted)}
  .page-footer-brand{font-size:7pt;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);letter-spacing:.06em}
  .page-footer-brand span{color:var(--gold)}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══════════════════════════ PAGE 1 ══════════════════════════════════════════
     Subject, Appraisal Values, Grade, Property Stats, Neighborhood, Admin Review
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="page">

  <!-- Brand header -->
  <div class="brand-bar">
    <div class="brand-left">
      <div class="brand-name">VISION <span>VMC</span></div>
      <div class="brand-sub">Real Estate Valuation Experts &bull; Licensed Nationally</div>
    </div>
    <div class="brand-badges">
      <span class="brand-badge">Desktop Appraisal Review — Non-Owner Occupied</span>
      <span class="brand-badge">Vision DVR-10 Form</span>
      <span class="brand-contact">info@visionvmc.com &bull; 425 Town Plaza Ave., Ponte Vedra, FL 32081</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Form title -->
  <div class="form-title-bar">
    <h1>Desktop Appraisal Review &mdash; Non-Owner Occupied</h1>
    <p>File No. {{metadata.orderNumber}} &bull; Loan No. {{metadata.loanNumber}} &bull; Vision VMC DVR-10</p>
  </div>

  <!-- SUBJECT -->
  <div class="section-hdr">Subject Property</div>
  <div class="row g2">
    <div class="cell">
      <span class="lbl">Street Address</span>
      <span class="val">{{streetAddress}}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cell">
      <span class="lbl">Loan ID / File No.</span>
      <span class="val">{{loanId}}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row g4">
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">City</span><span class="val">{{city}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">State</span><span class="val">{{state}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Zip Code</span><span class="val">{{zipCode}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell">
      <span class="lbl">Additional Analysis Recommended?</span>
      <span class="val">
        <span class="yn-pair">
          <span class="yn-box{{#if additionalAnalysisYes}} checked{{/if}}">&#10003;</span> Y
        </span>
        &nbsp;
        <span class="yn-pair">
          <span class="yn-box{{#unless additionalAnalysisYes}} checked{{/unless}}">&#10003;</span> N
        </span>
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row g3">
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Loan Purpose</span><span class="val">{{loanPurpose}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Prior Sale Price</span><span class="val">{{priorSalesPrice}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Date of Prior Sale</span><span class="val">{{priorSaleDate}}</span></div>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:6pt;font-style:italic;color:var(--muted);padding:2px 6px;margin-bottom:4px">
    *If home price appreciation is notably significant, please comment on page two regarding whether appreciation is due to market conditions and/or improvements to the subject property.
  </div>

  <!-- TOP: Photo + Values/Grade -->
  <div class="top-grid">

    <!-- LEFT: Subject photo -->
    <div>
      <div class="section-hdr gold" style="margin-top:0">Subject Photo</div>
      <div class="photo-box">
        {{#if subjectPhoto}}
        <img src="{{subjectPhoto.dataUri}}" alt="Subject Front">
        {{else}}
        <div class="photo-placeholder">SUBJECT<br>PROPERTY PHOTO</div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: Appraisal values + grade -->
    <div>
      <div class="section-hdr gold" style="margin-top:0">Appraisal Values &amp; Grade</div>

      <!-- Original Appraisal -->
      <div class="value-panel" style="margin-bottom:5px">
        <div class="value-panel-hdr">Original Appraisal</div>
        <div class="value-row">
          <span class="value-lbl">Opinion of Value</span>
          <div>
            <div class="value-val">{{originalAppraisalValue}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-row">
          <span class="value-lbl">Effective Date</span>
          <span class="value-val" style="font-size:8pt">{{originalAppraisalDate}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="value-row">
          <span class="value-lbl">Form Type</span>
          <span class="value-val" style="font-size:8pt">{{originalFormType}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review Value -->
      <div class="value-panel" style="margin-bottom:5px">
        <div class="value-panel-hdr">Review Opinion of Value</div>
        <div class="value-row">
          <span class="value-lbl">Review Value</span>
          <div>
            <div class="value-val">{{reviewValue}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-row">
          <span class="value-lbl">Review Date</span>
          <span class="value-val" style="font-size:8pt">{{reviewDate}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="value-row">
          <span class="value-lbl">% Variance</span>
          <span class="value-val" style="font-size:8pt">{{variancePct}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Appraisal Grade A–D -->
      <div class="grade-section">
        <div class="grade-hdr">Appraisal Grade</div>
        <div class="grade-row">
          <div class="grade-badge grade-A{{#if gradeIsA}} selected{{/if}}">
            <span class="grade-letter">A</span>
            <span class="grade-tick">{{#if gradeIsA}}&#10003;{{else}}&mdash;{{/if}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grade-badge grade-B{{#if gradeIsB}} selected{{/if}}">
            <span class="grade-letter">B</span>
            <span class="grade-tick">{{#if gradeIsB}}&#10003;{{else}}&mdash;{{/if}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grade-badge grade-C{{#if gradeIsC}} selected{{/if}}">
            <span class="grade-letter">C</span>
            <span class="grade-tick">{{#if gradeIsC}}&#10003;{{else}}&mdash;{{/if}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grade-badge grade-D{{#if gradeIsD}} selected{{/if}}">
            <span class="grade-letter">D</span>
            <span class="grade-tick">{{#if gradeIsD}}&#10003;{{else}}&mdash;{{/if}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grade-desc">
          <span><b>A</b> — Market value well supported; typically within 5%</span>
          <span><b>B</b> — Market value reasonably supported; within 10%</span>
          <span><b>C</b> — Market value not supported within 10%</span>
          <span><b>D</b> — Report incomplete / significant errors / not investment grade</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PROPERTY CHARACTERISTICS -->
  <div class="section-hdr">Property Characteristics</div>
  <div class="row g4">
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Property Type</span><span class="val">{{propertyType}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Condition</span><span class="val">{{condition}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Year Built</span><span class="val">{{yearBuilt}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Units</span><span class="val">{{units}}</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row g4">
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Total Rooms</span><span class="val">{{rooms}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Bedrooms</span><span class="val">{{bedrooms}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Bathrooms</span><span class="val">{{bathrooms}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Lot Size (Acres)</span><span class="val">{{lotSizeAcres}}</span></div>
  </div>

  <!-- NEIGHBORHOOD -->
  <div class="section-hdr">Neighborhood Characteristics</div>
  <div class="row g4">
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Location Type</span><span class="val">{{locationType}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Property Values</span><span class="val">{{propertyValues}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Demand / Supply</span><span class="val">{{demandSupply}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Marketing Time</span><span class="val">{{marketingTime}}</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="row g2">
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Quality</span><span class="val">{{quality}}</span></div>
    <div class="cell"><span class="lbl">Report Date</span><span class="val">{{reportDate}}</span></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ADMINISTRATIVE APPRAISAL REVIEW -->
  <div class="section-hdr">Administrative Appraisal Review</div>
  <div class="admin-row">
    <span class="admin-q-num">1</span>
    <span class="admin-q-text">Is the opinion of market value provided in the report adequately supported?</span>
    <span class="admin-yn">
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#if adminQ1}} checked{{/if}}">&#10003;</span> Y</span>
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#unless adminQ1}} checked{{/unless}}">&#10003;</span> N</span>
    </span>
  </div>
  <div class="admin-row">
    <span class="admin-q-num">2</span>
    <span class="admin-q-text">Are the comparable sales similar to the subject location, characteristics, and functionality?</span>
    <span class="admin-yn">
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#if adminQ2}} checked{{/if}}">&#10003;</span> Y</span>
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#unless adminQ2}} checked{{/unless}}">&#10003;</span> N</span>
    </span>
  </div>
  <div class="admin-row">
    <span class="admin-q-num">3</span>
    <span class="admin-q-text">Are the adjustments consistent and supported?</span>
    <span class="admin-yn">
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#if adminQ3}} checked{{/if}}">&#10003;</span> Y</span>
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#unless adminQ3}} checked{{/unless}}">&#10003;</span> N</span>
    </span>
  </div>
  <div class="admin-row">
    <span class="admin-q-num">4</span>
    <span class="admin-q-text">Are there any concerns with external influences?</span>
    <span class="admin-yn">
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#if adminQ4}} checked{{/if}}">&#10003;</span> Y</span>
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#unless adminQ4}} checked{{/unless}}">&#10003;</span> N</span>
    </span>
  </div>
  <div class="admin-row">
    <span class="admin-q-num">5</span>
    <span class="admin-q-text">Is the information in the improvements section complete and accurate?</span>
    <span class="admin-yn">
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#if adminQ5}} checked{{/if}}">&#10003;</span> Y</span>
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#unless adminQ5}} checked{{/unless}}">&#10003;</span> N</span>
    </span>
  </div>
  <div class="admin-row">
    <span class="admin-q-num">6</span>
    <span class="admin-q-text">Does the neighborhood section reflect any negative attributes that would affect value? (comment required if yes)</span>
    <span class="admin-yn">
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#if adminQ6}} checked{{/if}}">&#10003;</span> Y</span>
      <span class="yn-pair"><span class="yn-box{{#unless adminQ6}} checked{{/unless}}">&#10003;</span> N</span>
    </span>
  </div>

  <div class="page-footer">
    <span class="page-footer-left">Desktop Appraisal Review &mdash; NOO &bull; File {{metadata.orderNumber}} &bull; Page 1 of 4</span>
    <span class="page-footer-brand">VISION <span>VMC</span> &bull; Real Estate Valuation Experts</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════ PAGE 2 ══════════════════════════════════════════
     Reviewer Comments + Scope of Work (Part 1)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="page">

  <div class="brand-bar">
    <div class="brand-left">
      <div class="brand-name">VISION <span>VMC</span></div>
      <div class="brand-sub">Real Estate Valuation Experts &bull; Licensed Nationally</div>
    </div>
    <div class="brand-badges">
      <span class="brand-badge">Reviewer Comments &amp; Scope of Work</span>
      <span class="brand-contact">File No. {{metadata.orderNumber}}</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-hdr">Reviewer Comments</div>
  <div style="font-size:7pt;font-style:italic;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px">
    If answers from page one impact value please comment below.
  </div>
  <div class="comments-box">{{comments}}</div>

  <div class="section-hdr">Review Appraiser's Scope of Work, Limiting Conditions &amp; Certification</div>

  <div class="scope-para">
    <strong>Intended Use:</strong> The intended use of this desk review is to determine whether the appraisal value is supported within 10%, to provide a review value and a percentage variance between the two values (if there is one), and to identify/comment on any deficiencies evident in the original appraisal.
  </div>

  <div class="scope-para">
    <strong>Intended User:</strong> The intended user of this desk review is the lender/client.
  </div>

  <div class="scope-para">
    <strong>Definition of Market Value:</strong> The most probable price which a property should bring in a competitive and open market under all conditions requisite to a fair sale, the buyer and seller, each acting prudently, knowledgeably and assuming the price is not affected by undue stimulus. Implicit in this definition is the consummation of a sale as of a specified date and the passing of title from seller to buyer under conditions whereby:
  </div>

  <div class="scope-para indent">
    (1) buyer and seller are typically motivated.<br>
    (2) both parties are well informed or well advised, and each acting in what he or she considers his or her own best interest.<br>
    (3) a reasonable time is allowed for exposure in the open market.<br>
    (4) payment is made in terms of cash in U.S. dollars or in terms of financial arrangements comparable thereto.<br>
    (5) the price represents the normal consideration for the property sold unaffected by special or creative financing or sales concessions* granted by anyone associated with the sale.
  </div>

  <div class="scope-para">
    *Adjustments to the comparables must be made for special or creative financing or sales concessions. No adjustments are necessary for those costs which are normally paid by sellers as a result of tradition or law in a market area; these costs are readily identifiable since the seller pays these costs in virtually all sales transactions. Special or creative financing adjustments can be made to the comparable property by comparisons to financing terms offered by a third-party institutional lender that is not already involved with the property or transaction. Any adjustment should not be calculated
  </div>

